{"tid":921398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK No IT！新建校舍採購清單 仍有大電視、卡式錄音機、電動打字機及傳真機等","createTime":"2018-11-29T13:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T18:57:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ff79ffb549ee1d0b6d14223f509abe32a7da4343","tid":921398,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181129/s00001/abf9e302b3b8583a4e8a60a35ca20cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181129%2Fs00001%2Fabf9e302b3b8583a4e8a60a35ca20cbc.jpg&h=7ee85828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時新建官津學校需按教育局的「新建校舍家具及設備一覽表（F&amp;E）」購買所需設備。立法會教育界議員葉建源表示，現時一覽表雖有更新，但多項內容未有「與時並進」修訂，如幻燈機及手提卡式收音錄音機等，學校如要購買清單以外物品，要額外搜集資料等再交教育局逐項審批，變相花更多時間。    <br />\n<br />\n「新建校舍家具及設備一覽表」今學年的費用總額為234.7萬元，如新校修訂的清單建議超過標準，學校需要調低其他項目金額或自行承擔等。葉建源表示，清單今年雖有更新，惟當中仍有不少項目為「古代」物品，如29吋彩色大電視連推架、電動打字機及數據傳真機等，如學校要另外購買，要自行搜集資料、格價、招標，經法團校董會通過修訂項目後，再交局方逐項審批。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181129/s00001/1543469271021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181129%2Fs00001%2F1543469271021&d=Myni4mpKaVLfVJ%2F686klHUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=66233d3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181129%2Fs00001%2F1543469271021&h=edd0585e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181129/s00001/1543469271021</a>"},{"pid":"da980f7d5fbe411c56dc726b020e4252a9da889e","tid":921398,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" c